              <li>‚Ä¢ Order management system</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <div class="bg-pink-100 rounded-lg p-8 text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-4">üßÅ</div>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Beautiful product showcase with online ordering</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-8">
          <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">SEO & Local Marketing</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Optimized the website for local search and implemented a comprehensive SEO strategy to increase visibility.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Local SEO optimization</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Google My Business setup</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Content marketing strategy</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Review management</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-1/2">
