            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
          <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Social Media Marketing</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Created engaging social media campaigns showcasing delicious cupcakes and building a loyal community.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Instagram and Facebook marketing</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Content creation and photography</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Influencer partnerships</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Customer engagement campaigns</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <div class="bg-purple-100 rounded-lg p-8 text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-4">üì±</div>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Engaging social media presence</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Results Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">The Results</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
          Within 6 months, Bella's Cupcakes saw remarkable growth across all digital channels.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-pink-600 mb-2">300%</div>
