    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <blockquote class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 italic mb-6">
        "Proximo Digital transformed our small bakery into a thriving online business. The e-commerce website they built is beautiful and easy to use, and our online orders have increased by 300%! We couldn't be happier with the results."
      </blockquote>
